[SN]TITLE[SN]
Wales Sports Personality Dan Biggar's 'dance'

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
His match-winning kicks to beat England 28-25 in the 2015 Rugby World Cup thrilled Wales fans and helped fly-half Dan Biggar win the public vote to become BBC Cymru Wales Sports Personality of the Year.

